Something is happening.

66
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:49,200
Out through door and pretend to write. I wrote on the paper all the way out.

67
00:06:57,040 --> 00:07:00,080
- Did you go out, Jinny? -Yes.

68
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:04,760
Did you plug it in? Do you know that you got a link?

69
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:09,600
- It flashed. - It hasn't come up yet.

70
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:15,560
Forget it. It came up! It's up. Yes, we have contact!

71
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:20,360
Holy shit!

72
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:24,960
Oh! How fucking nervous I was.

73
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:27,480
So fucking good!

74
