Like, fuck.

75
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:33,240
The glasses were foggy all the time.

76
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:38,240
She's a fucking hero. I'm on a parking lot, so I'll pull away.

77
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:45,080
Feel free to start Responder in analyze mode, right away.

78
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:51,880
There's a risk that he ... When I said what wanted to do, he paused.

79
