88
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:15,000
While Linus is investigating the company from the inside -

89
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:19,520
- they meet with the company's CEO to discuss the assignment.

90
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:23,400
The CEO does not know that the hackers have jumpstarted.

91
