We start to map out what is there. We clearly see people going home.

155
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:18,680
We have no success. The attacks which we normally use do not work.

156
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:21,680
I'm wondering if we should test–

157
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:25,960
-to do an active Responder on ONE computer.

158
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:31,280
