160
00:15:35,640 --> 00:15:39,560
We have a program which will run overnight–

161
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:42,880
-And when they come to the office tomorrow.

162
00:15:43,040 --> 00:15:48,280
Hopefully someone has a laptop with them that they had brought home.

163
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:54,280
When they start it, it will hopefully trigger something that we can catch.

164
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:58,680
There is a reason to stay late.

165
00:15:58,840 --> 00:16:02,240
You can do bolder things on the network -

166
00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:06,400
- without worrying about people noticing it.

167
00:16:06,560 --> 00:16:10,120
So there is every reason to stay late.

168
00:16:35,800 --> 00:16:40,960
Ransomware attacks are common, but a crime that few want to talk about.

169
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:46,120
SVT has asked several companies subjected to major attacks -

170
00:16:46,280 --> 00:16:50,680
- but none of them want to line up for an interview.

171
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:54,200
Nobody knows how common it is–

172
00:16:54,360 --> 00:16:58,600
