173
00:16:58,760 --> 00:17:03,760
It may be that they think that the police will do nothing -

174
00:17:03,920 --> 00:17:08,600
-Or that you do not want to broadcast that you have had an attack -

175
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:13,120
-Which has hit hard, because companies think it would mean-

176
00:17:13,280 --> 00:17:20,000
-That "we show that we have bad security and get no customers ".

177
00:17:38,320 --> 00:17:42,080
We have to be a bit more structured now.

178
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:46,160
- For Responder ... -Responder has no hits.

179
00:17:46,320 --> 00:17:50,680
