They may very well have some tech nerd who've made sure they are safe.

184
00:18:11,640 --> 00:18:16,560
It's a disaster for us. Then we have to get very creative.

185
00:18:20,720 --> 00:18:25,800
In the worst case you had a good idea there, Linus.

186
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:33,000
Trying to poison the network and force a machine to connect to us.

187
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:38,320
Maybe we should perform a bolder attack anyway.

188
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:42,720
With bolder I mean: If we're looking for something in a forest

189
00:18:42,880 --> 00:18:47,840
- then we'll blow away all the trees to find something on the ground.

190
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:53,760
Jesper's attack will possibly stop the network from working -

191
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:56,720
-For the ones we attack.

192
00:18:56,880 --> 00:19:03,280
Our tiny computer, which we have hidden behind a cupboard inside the company ...

193
