Nobody remembers a coward. Shall we press all three?

196
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:22,800
-Shared responsibility is not responsibility. - You have full power.

197
00:19:22,960 --> 00:19:26,080
I'll press now, then.

198
00:19:29,920 --> 00:19:33,120
