199
00:19:33,280 --> 00:19:36,640
Yes! New hash. Damn, what a treat.

200
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:42,720
Come on now!

201
00:19:42,880 --> 00:19:46,520
It will be seen, this is noisy.

202
