Yes, and it does.

203
00:19:49,360 --> 00:19:51,880
–Oh, oh. - What?

204
00:19:52,040 --> 00:19:56,680
- Have you found a net? Min session är nere.

205
00:19:56,840 --> 00:19:59,080
-No no no....

206
